<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">I am wondering if there are any non-robe chest pieces that a wizard can wear that will look good with Black Chitin Legs.  I just recently aquired some GEBs and I took my robe off to see what they looked like with the leggins, and I really liked the look. I shifted some gear around so that I could still have 200 int, but I would like to have something in that slot.  Preferebly something black.  I'm sure that is probably not going to happen though.  I'm thinking maybe netted, or mesh, if I can wear it.  I would prefer something with stats, but looks are the most important here.  <p>

I know some of you may think it's crazy to be a wizard w/o a robe, but I am sick of wearing a dress.  I guess if I ever get carmine I'll go back to it, but if I can find a piece that will look good on me for my chest slot.  My SMR will have to sit in my inventory most the time.  Welcoming all suggestions and flames.<hr>Parlan Blakstone  <br>
52 Wizard of E'ci</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
